Project Title: Age Calculator

Description:

This project provides a simple and effective age calculator that calculates the age based on the user's birth date. It offers a user-friendly interface for easy input and accurate output.

Features:

Date Input: Allows users to enter their birth date in a convenient format.
Age Calculation: Accurately calculates the age in years, months, and days.
Error Handling: Validates the input to ensure the entered date is a valid date.
Clear Output: Displays the calculated age in a readable format.
